frontend.components.factorys

Class StructogramFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • frontend.components.factorys.StructogramFactory

  • public final class StructogramFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory for structogram components. Creates an entity, a visualisation object, and add the entity to the structogram, according to the position of selected statement in the visual object (before, after, instead of)
